verbose_text: We found that the effects of oscillatory treatment with 2 x 10 -6 M CORT on the cell cycle in NSPC was indistinguishable from that of oscillatory treatment with 1 x 10 -6 M CORT, indicating that GC amplitudes that fully activate the GR result in similar effects on the cell cycle in NSPC.
evidence: GC amplitudes that fully activate the GR
